data.title: 1764) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Abigail Rowley, dau. of Samuel Rowley and Elizabeth Fuller, b. of record Feb. 13, 1716/17 at Hebron, Conn. She d. Oct. 23, 1764 at Hebron, Æ 48 (g.s.)  Abigail was a multiple Mayflower descendant through the Fuller ancestry. Her mother, Elizabeth (Fuller) Rowley, was the dau. of John,3 (aka little John) Fuller...
